About Us

Chiliz is a global fintech and blockchain company behind Socios.com the world’s first fan voting and rewards app.

We have partnered with more than 160 of the most recognizable sports and esports brands in the world to provide a blockchain-backed solution to boosting fan engagement.

Our partners include - The Los Angeles Lakers, New England Patriots, Paris Saint-Germain, Juventus, FC Barcelona, Atlético de Madrid, UFC, Brooklyn Nets, Galatasaray, Golden State Warriors, Manchester City FC, Davis Cup , and many more.

Our diverse and extraordinary team - that spans 30+ nationalities - are the driving force behind our success with creative thinking at the heart of anything and everything we do.

OUR BRANDS & CHANNELS

Chiliz ($CHZ) is our blockchain and digital currency, which powers Socios.com.

Socios.com is the world's first fan voting and rewards platform. We produce digital assets called Fan Tokens for our partner teams, which fans use to vote in team-specific polls to earn rewards and once-in-a-lifetime experiences.

Chiliz.net is a first-of-its-kind mobile and desktop crypto exchange for sports & entertainment products.

Responsibilities & Duties

Comfortable in creating copy from scratch and taking campaigns from ideation to implementation;
Be the main lead in spicing up the Socios.com app with fan content, competitions, quizzes and games;
Create, produce and manage high-quality content and assets through the liaison with the internal marketing teams and creative services teams;Research and coordinate the creative elements for your content and suggest inspirations for images, graphics, videos, and other artwork;
Passionate about performance, making sure that you deliver content that is not only engaging but that ultimately converts and/or retains users on the Socios.com app ;
Be a hawkeye - make sure you have an eye for detail and that you are keen on proofreading before posting material;
Work in a multidisciplinary team with professionals such as designers, marketing execs, videographers and creative minds to improve your team’s content strategy;
Adhere to copyright and privacy standards and company policies;
Keep abreast with new trends in web technology.

Skills & Requirements

A minimum of two years experience writing for marketing, preferably in the sports industry;
Must be creative, be prepared to think outside-the-box;
Must be passionate about all sports;
Must be passionate about performance, ensuring that content is not only engaging but that ultimately converts and/or retains users on the Socios.com app;
Must have an eye for detail and be a perfectionist;
Must enjoy working in a multidisciplinary team with professionals such as designers, marketing execs, videographers, and creative minds to maximise the content strategy;
Must possess the right knowledge around tracking and attribution;
Knowledge of / interest in digital currencies, blockchain considered an asset

What We Offer

From receiving your application to joining us on this fantastic journey, our recruitment process is a fun and agile 3 step process, meaning that you won’t be left waiting to get an answer.

You’ll start off with an interview with one of our dedicated HR team members, you’ll then be given an assessment before a final stage interview with the hiring manager.

From working with some of the biggest and most recognisable sports teams in the world to creating unforgettable fan experiences, all while using blockchain technology, it’s never a dull day here at Chiliz.

You have the flexibility to split your time between working from home or from one of our beautiful offices in Madrid, Miami, London, Istanbul, Lyon, Gzira, or São Paulo, located at the very heart of these vibrant and cosmopolitan cities. And if there’s no office close to you, we’re cool with fully remote working too!

We’re an extraordinary multi-cultural team spanning 30+ nationalities with ideas as diverse and interesting as we are.

Professional and personal development are very important to us and our package includes, depending on location and contractual agreement, a wellness allowance, private healthcare and a pension plan.

Together with a supportive and collaborative working environment and great company perks, above all, we give you the chance to be a part of the future.

